Ticketing System

Signup User:

1. Create user with basic information
2. have two types of users(Admin, Customer)
3. User email should be unique across user

APIs
Create user
update user
deactivate user

Ticket operation

1. create ticket with info like(Ticket id, Subject, Message, priority)
2. only valid user can create ticket
3. only admin user can close or resolve the ticket with reason
4. user with customer type can only reopen the ticket
5. only resolved state tickets can be reopened
6. Admin can reply to the query and the customer can also reply,
   chain of comments should be maintained for the each tickets
7. comments should be maintained in separate collection associated with ticket id

APIs
create ticket
update ticket
Add reply
close/resolve ticket